{"title":"ES6：语法及新特性","uid":"ab2e04325ebb401c12b2a873d21b4d82","slug":"ES6","date":"2021-02-08T13:45:13.000Z","updated":"2021-02-09T05:40:33.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ES6.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/u=589076168,2353171091&fm=26&gp=0.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"ES6：语法及新特性\"><a href=\"#ES6：语法及新特性\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ES6：语法及新特性\"></a>ES6：语法及新特性</h2><h3 id=\"let变量\"><a href=\"#let变量\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"let变量\"></a>let变量</h3><ul>\n<li><p>let不能重复声明</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>块级作用域，只能在代码段中有效</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>不存在变量提升（不允许声明之前使用）</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-js\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"language-js\">console.log(x);\nlet x &#x3D; &#39;hello&#39; &#x2F;&#x2F;不允许</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>不影响作用域链</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-js\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"language-js\">&#123;\n    let x &#x3D; &#39;hello&#39;;\n    function fun()&#123;\n        console.log(x);\n    &#125;\n    fun();\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"const声明常量\"><a href=\"#const声明常量\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"const声明常量\"></a>const声明常量</h3><ul>\n<li><p>一定要赋初值</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>常量不能修改</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>块级作用域</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>对数组和对象的元素修改，不算做对常量的修改，不会报错</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-js\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"language-js\">const TEAM &#x3D; &#123;&#39;UZI&#39;,&#39;MING&#39;&#125;;\nTAEM.push(&#39;LETME&#39;);</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"解构赋值\"><a href=\"#解构赋值\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解构赋值\"></a>解构赋值</h3><ul>\n<li><p>ES6允许按照一定模式从数组和对象中提取值，对变量进行赋值</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>数组的解构</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-js\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"language-js\">const F4 &#x3D; [&#39;小沈阳&#39;,&#39;刘能&#39;,&#39;赵四&#39;,&#39;宋小宝&#39;];\nlet [xiao,liu,zhao,song] &#x3D; F4;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>对象的解构</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-js\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"language-js\">const zhao &#x3D; &#123;\n    name: &#39;赵本山&#39;,\n    age: &#39;不详&#39;,\n    xiaopin: function()&#123;\n        console.log(&quot;hello&quot;);\n    &#125;\n&#125;\nlet &#123;name,age,xiaopin&#125; &#x3D; zhao;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"模板字符串\"><a href=\"#模板字符串\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"模板字符串\"></a>模板字符串</h3><ul>\n<li><p>用反引号声明字符串</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-js\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"language-js\">let str &#x3D; &#96;hello&#96;;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>内容中可以细节出现换行符</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-js\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"language-js\">let str &#x3D; &#96;hello\n\t\t\tworld&#96;;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>变量拼接</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-js\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"language-js\">let str1 &#x3D; &#39;hello&#39;;\nlet str2 &#x3D; &#96;$&#123;str1&#125;world&#96;;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"箭头函数\"><a href=\"#箭头函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"箭头函数\"></a>箭头函数</h3><ul>\n<li><p>声明</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-js\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"language-js\">let fun &#x3D; (a,b) &#x3D;&gt; &#123;\n    return a+b;\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>this是静态的，this始终指向函数声明时所在作用域下的this的值</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>不能作为构造实例化对象</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>不能使用argument变量</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>箭头函数的简写</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-js\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"language-js\">&#x2F;&#x2F;省略小括号，当形参有且只有一个的时候\nlet add &#x3D; n &#x3D;&gt;&#123;\n    return n+n;\n&#125;\n&#x2F;&#x2F;省略花括号，当代码体只有一条语句的时候，此时return必须省略，而且语句的执行结果就是函数的返回值\nlet pow &#x3D; n &#x3D;&gt; n*n;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"rest参数\"><a href=\"#rest参数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"rest参数\"></a>rest参数</h3><ul>\n<li><p>rest参数必须放在最后</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-js\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"language-js\">function fun(a,b,...args)&#123;\n    console.log(a);\n    console.log(b);\n    consoel.log(args);\n&#125;\nfun(1,2,3,4,5);</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"扩展运算符能将数组转化为逗号分隔得参数序列\"><a href=\"#扩展运算符能将数组转化为逗号分隔得参数序列\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"扩展运算符能将数组转化为逗号分隔得参数序列\"></a>扩展运算符能将数组转化为逗号分隔得参数序列</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-js\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"language-js\">const args &#x3D; [&#39;hello&#39;,&#39;world&#39;];\nfunction fun()&#123;\n    console.log(arguments);\n&#125;\nfun(...args);&#x2F;&#x2F;等价于fun(&#39;hello&#39;,&#39;world&#39;);</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"Symbol基本使用\"><a href=\"#Symbol基本使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Symbol基本使用\"></a>Symbol基本使用</h3>","feature":true,"text":"ES6：语法及新特性let变量 let不能重复声明 块级作用域，只能在代码段中有效 不存在变量提升（不允许声明之前使用） console.log(x); let x &#x3D; &#39;hello&#39; &#x2F;&#x2F;不允许 不影响作用域链 &#123; let...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.6k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":1,"path":"api/categories/前端.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":11,"path":"api/tags/前端.json"},{"name":"ES6","slug":"ES6","count":1,"path":"api/tags/ES6.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#ES6%EF%BC%9A%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%8A%E6%96%B0%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7\"><span class=\"toc-text\">ES6：语法及新特性</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#let%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">let变量</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#const%E5%A3%B0%E6%98%8E%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">const声明常量</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%84%E8%B5%8B%E5%80%BC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">解构赋值</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">模板字符串</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AE%AD%E5%A4%B4%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">箭头函数</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=